---
import Button from "@/components/ui/Button.astro";
import Container from "@/components/ui/Container.astro";
---

<section class="relative min-h-screen flex items-center -mt-16 md:-mt-20 overflow-hidden bg-black">
  <!-- Background image -->
  <div
    class="absolute inset-0 bg-cover bg-center bg-no-repeat opacity-60"
    style="background-image: url('/images/hero-bg.jpg');"
  />
  <div class="absolute inset-0 bg-gradient-to-r from-black/80 via-black/50 to-transparent"></div>

  <Container class="relative z-10">
    <div class="max-w-2xl pt-20">
      <h1
        class="hero-title text-4xl md:text-5xl lg:text-6xl font-extrabold leading-tight text-white"
      >
        가장 쉬운 AI 교육
      </h1>

      <p
        class="hero-subtitle mt-5 text-lg md:text-xl font-bold text-white"
      >
        공공기관과 대기업이 선택한 AI 교육 파트너!
      </p>

      <p
        class="hero-description mt-3 text-base md:text-lg text-gray-300 leading-relaxed"
      >
        저희는 한국에서 다양한 기관과 기업을 대상으로,
        <br />
        GPT부터 최신 생성형 AI까지 실무 중심의 교육을 제공합니다.
      </p>

      <div class="hero-cta mt-8">
        <Button href="/contact/" size="lg" class="px-12">
          지금 알아보기
        </Button>
      </div>
    </div>
  </Container>
</section>

<style>
  .hero-title,
  .hero-subtitle,
  .hero-description,
  .hero-cta {
    opacity: 0;
    animation: fadeInUp 0.7s ease-out forwards;
  }

  .hero-title {
    animation-delay: 0s;
  }

  .hero-subtitle {
    animation-delay: 0.15s;
  }

  .hero-description {
    animation-delay: 0.25s;
  }

  .hero-cta {
    animation-delay: 0.35s;
  }

  @keyframes fadeInUp {
    from {
      opacity: 0;
      transform: translateY(30px);
    }
    to {
      opacity: 1;
      transform: translateY(0);
    }
  }
</style>
